discourse_list.title: View all Dai Savings Rate deposits and withdrawals

content.content: This URL displays all the Dai Savings Rate Deposits that have occurred since this version was launched on 11/18/19. https://EtherLogs.com/EHt This URL shows all the DSR Withdrawals: https://EtherLogs.com/oXI From either webpage, you can view the following information:   To see the Ethereum address of any user, click an address in the Click To Show Ethereum Address column. The next screen will show the user’s Ethereum address in the first transaction (unless the user was a contract). Click that Ethereum address to see their Etherscan page.   To see the transactions with the HIghest and Lowest Dai Amounts, change the Sort Field to “Dai Amount”.   To see unique users, change the Sort Field to “Click To Sho…”, and then click [Show Distinct].
